description:
AMeiToken is a new gaming community based on the CIS economy. Let gamers become community owners and share community development dividends.

AMT combined with blockchain distributed storage technology features decentralization, trustworthiness, traceability, data not tampering, peer-to-peer payment, wisdom

Ability to contract and other characteristics. Can make information more transparent, more real, more efficient, fair, just, open consumer experience, make more virtual networks

Consumers have no worries. Create a global blockchain game ecosystem dedicated to promoting standardized trading of virtual assets and blockchain

The world's leading ecological community in the gaming industry.
